				<h1>MediCare.AI</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">Intelligent Patient Engagement Platform</p>

				<h2>The Problem</h2>
				<p>
					Medical and dental practices face overwhelming administrative overhead managing patient 
					inquiries, appointment scheduling, test result queries, and basic clinic information 
					across multiple communication channels. Front desk staff spend 60-70% of their time on 
					repetitive questions, leading to long wait times, frustrated patients, and inefficient 
					resource allocation.
				</p>

				<h2>The Solution</h2>
				<p>
					MediCare.AI is an enterprise-grade AI assistant that automates patient services using 
					LangGraph and LangChain. The platform provides 24/7 intelligent support across WhatsApp, 
					Telegram, and Instagram, handling appointments, doctor availability, test results, and 
					clinic information through natural conversation.
				</p>

				<h2>Key Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Multi-Channel Support</strong>: Seamless integration with WhatsApp, Telegram, and Instagram for unified patient communication</li>
					<li><strong>Appointment Management</strong>: AI-powered scheduling, rescheduling, and cancellation with calendar integration</li>
					<li><strong>Doctor Availability</strong>: Real-time schedule checking and slot recommendations</li>
					<li><strong>Test Results Tracking</strong>: Secure retrieval and explanation of lab reports and diagnostic results</li>
					<li><strong>RAG Architecture</strong>: Accurate information retrieval from clinic knowledge base</li>
					<li><strong>Patient Data Validation</strong>: Robust verification and privacy protection</li>
				</ul>

